The annotation goes between #[derive(...)] and pub struct:

#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize)]
#[serde(rename_all = "camelCase")]
pub struct StructName {
    ...
}

Do NOT rename the Rust field names themselves.
The annotation only affects JSON serialisation.
Internal Rust code continues to use snake_case.

